This configuration of Input contains:

- Mono
- Narrow
- Regular weight (for the non-bold non-italic face)
- double-storey a
- single-storey g
- i and l with top serifs and no bottom serifs
- slashed zero
- centered asterisk
- recurve braces
- 1.2x line spacing

Note that, because Input's license forbids redistribution, I cannot include the font in this repo. The PKGBUILD will download it from the source site. You may want to save a copy of the zip archive just in case it ever goes away.
